有竞争性。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-8ab60942096e50993600dbd0deb89933_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/623595456"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIh++V97O86blZEAMaCTEwMDg1NjAzMSDCj8GoBjAAOL8EQDByCTYyMzU5NTQ1NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1696133340.543730", "card_id": "Q_610904836", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "「我突然留意到自己走神了」，这种「回过神」的注意转移既非主动又非被动，它的驱动机制和神经机制是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如果注意分主动目标指向和被动刺激驱动。在手头没有任务的时候，或者就是坐在那任凭默认网络胡思乱想，注意对象突然从白日梦的内容转移到「身心状态」上，既不是来自一种新异的刺激，也不是来自主动地集中注意，这种注意转移活动的驱动机制和生理机制是什么？ 有时看电影看的入迷，沉浸到剧情里，突然意识到自己正在看电影，正在有兴奋或开心的情绪，好像也是同一种心理活动。都不是刻意转移注意，如何理解这种觉知意识？ 我同意白日梦和沉浸电影剧情都是大脑进入潜意识的自动驾驶，但我好奇的是在明显没有新异刺激的情况下、而且不带有明确目的，大脑自动从潜意识状态又恢复意识，是什么力量或机制驱动它跳出潜意识的，生物意义在哪？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-6c24cf7bf0f969e41220b07205e61e92_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/610904836"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ih++V97O86blZEAMaCDk4MDM3NDYwIOjXn6UGMAA49ARAMXIJNjEwOTA0ODM2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1683447529524715520", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/org/pi-yao-qian-xian", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTY4MzQ0NzUyOTUyNDcxNTUyMHITMTY4MzQ0NzUyOTUyNDcxNTUyMHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}}